<i>noun</i>: 건의서 [거ː늬서/거ː니서] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>건의서 [거ː늬서/거ː니서]</dt><br>
<dd>petition; memorial; representation; recommendation</dd><br>
<dd>건의의 내용을 적은 문서.</dd><br>
<dd>A document containing details of a petition, memorial, or a recommendation.</dd><br>
